title: Uptown--1 block to the Lakes
posting_body: ['Nice 1 bedroom unit has bright updated kitchen and living area, lots of light, wood floors, just one block to the Lakes.', "You can't beat the location of the wonderful brick brownstone buildings at 1709-1715 Lagoon Avenue within walking distance of the lakes and all of Uptown's amazing restaurants, coffee shops, nightlife, boutiques, national stores, salons, grocery stores, and movie theatres.", 'Walk, bike, kayak at the Lakes just one block away.', 'Work out at CorePower Yoga, Lifetime Fitness, and the YWCA.', 'Minutes to downtown with easy access to bike on the Greenway or take the bus.', 'Includes heat, water and trash.', 'USI internet available, off-street parking, on-site laundry and storage, cats are permitted.', 'Call Jim at', 'show contact info', 'to set up your appointment today!', 'Available November 1.']
